      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an AI Sales Consultant.\n\nAnalyze the lead below and provide a short business assessment.\n\nName: {{ $json.Name }}\nCompany: {{ $json['Company name'] }}\nIndustry: {{ $json.Industry }}\nCompany Size: {{ $json['Company size'] }}\nMonthly Revenue: {{ $json['Monthly Revenue'] }}\nAutomation Request: {{ $json['What would you like to automate?'] }}\nTimeline: {{ $json['  How soon do you want a solution?  '] }}\n\nLead Score: {{ $json.lead_score }}\nLead Status: {{ $json.lead_status }}\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON.\n\n{\n\"reason\":\"\",\n\"priority\":\"\",\n\"recommended_action\":\"\"\n}\n\nRules:\n\npriority must be:\nHigh\nMedium\nLow\n\nrecommended_action must be one short sentence.\n\nreason must be one short sentence explaining why this lead is qualified.\n",
